{
  "stem": "13655.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They was killed there by the Germans, by the Polish watchmen, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but I escaped a lot of times.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to jump out, run out through the window.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The houses were smaller houses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One family had, like, a-- and I used to jump out of it and end up through the window, and I went out from the city-- a mile, two miles, whatever.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After they left, then I went back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They had a list.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They was asking to give them a list, how many people-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] --lives in that town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They gave them a list, the rabbi with a [INAUDIBLE] [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] --from the [INAUDIBLE], from the Jewish organization, and they took the list and brought them there, 18 miles to Biala Podlaska.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was the residents from the state.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All the Jews.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They went and they came at night, and they went from house to house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a man.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took them out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans, with Ukrainians, with Polish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With their helpers.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did this at night, and then in the daytime, in the morning, 6, 7 o'clock, 8 o'clock, they took them to the-- they had to go 20 miles, walking.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of them, sometimes, was a truck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But sometimes they had to-- they went by foot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That time, was my two brother-in-laws, they took them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they sent them away to Belzec.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] They was there a few weeks, and they came back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Somehow they sneaked out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't know where they're taking them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But when they came to the place, where they stopped already to arrive, that they know where they are.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
